Notes: UW-W is the #1 seed and received a first round bye. UW-S is the #4 seed and
defeated UW-River Falls 63-46 to advance into the semifinal.
The Warhawks advance to the WIAC Championship to face UW-Stevens Point in
Kachel Gym in Whitewater Sunday afternoon.
